The Beijing News Special Planning Editor Chen Wanting, proofread by Wu Xingfa, February 23, 2020, issued No.1, Wuhan Municipal New Crown Pneumonia Control and Prevention Command issued Notice No.1 to control the spread of the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic.
恢复时间另行通告。
Recovery time will be announced separately.
