In the afternoon, Wuhan Caidian Fire Goddess Hospital, a special hospital, was set up to treat patients with pneumonia in Wuhan, following the model of the Beijing Xiaotangshan Hospital during the 2003 SARS fight.
19时，湖北省召开新冠肺炎疫情防控工作新闻发布会。
At 19: 00, Hubei Province held a new crown pneumonia prevention and control work press conference.
湖北省文化和旅游厅党组成员、副厅长徐勇在会上表示，即日起，武汉市经营性文化娱乐场所暂停营业。
Xu Yong, deputy director and member of the party group of Hubei Provincial Culture and Tourism Administration, said at the meeting that the business cultural and entertainment venues in Wuhan were temporarily closed.
