2月15日晚间，新京报记者就此事向中国科学院武汉病毒研究所研究员石正丽、流感病毒实验室研究员陈全姣求证。
On the evening of Feb. 15, Xinhua News reporter Shi Zhengli, a researcher at Wuhan Institute of Virus of the Chinese Academy of Sciences, and Chen Quan Jiao, a researcher at the influenza virus laboratory.
两人均表示，对病毒所是否有一位名叫黄燕玲的女研究生并不掌握，但可以保证武汉病毒所目前无一人感染新冠肺炎。
Both said they did not know if the institute had a female graduate student named Huang Yanling, but there was no guarantee that none of the Wuhan virus patients were currently infected with pneumonia.
━━━━━-2月16日-正月廿三截至当日24时，全国累计报告确诊病例70548例，死亡1770例，治愈出院10844例。
Feb. 16 - January 23 At 2400 hours on the same day, a total of 70,548 confirmed cases and 1,770 deaths had been reported nationwide, and 10,844 cases had been cured.
湖北省累计报告确诊病例58182例（武汉市41152例），死亡1696例（武汉市1309例），治愈出院6639例。
A total of 58182 confirmed cases (41,152 in Wuhan) and 1,696 deaths (1,309 in Wuhan) were reported in Hubei Province, and 6,639 cases were cured.
△江汉区花楼街，雪后初晴，一名行人张开双臂享受阳光。
A pedestrian enjoys the sunshine with open arms after snow on Flower House Street in JiangHan District.
摄影/中青报·中青网记者鲁冲焦点事件▼国家卫健委新闻发言人米锋在国务院联防联控机制新闻发布会上表示，截至2月15日24时，湖北、全国其他省份重症病例占确诊病例的比例均明显下降。
As of 2400 Feb. 15, the proportion of serious cases in Hubei and other provinces nationwide had dropped noticeably, spokesman for the National Health Protection Commission said at a press conference.
湖北发布进一步强化新冠肺炎疫情防控的通告。
Hubei issued a notice to further strengthen the prevention and control of New Crown Pneumonia.
其中指出，城乡所有村组、社区、小区、居民点实行24小时最严格的封闭式管理。
It is pointed out that all village groups, communities, small areas and settlements in urban and rural areas are under the strictest 24-hour closed management.
严管外来车辆，非必需不进出；严管外来人员，非必要不入内；严管住户外出，药品和必需生活物品等可采取集中采购配送等方式进行。
Strict control of foreign vehicles, non-essential access; strict control of foreign personnel, it is necessary to enter; strict household out, drugs and essential goods can be procurement and distribution of centralized means.
针对网上热议的“武汉病毒所一研究生系零号病人”的信息，中国科学院武汉病毒研究所回应零号病人传闻：黄燕玲身体健康，未曾被感染。
In response to a heated online discussion about "Wuhan Virus Institute of a graduate student department zero patients", the Wuhan Institute of Virus Research of the Chinese Academy of Sciences responded to patient zero rumors: Huang Yanling is healthy and has not been infected.
━━━━━-2月17日-正月廿四截至当日24时，全国累计报告确诊病例72436例（新疆生产建设兵团核增2例），死亡1868例，治愈出院12552例（北京核增7例）。
February 17 - January 24 As of 2400 hours on the same day, a total of 72,436 confirmed cases (2 cases of nuclear increase in the Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps) had been reported, 1,868 deaths had been reported, and 12,552 cases of discharge had been cured (7 cases of nuclear increase in Beijing).
湖北省累计报告确诊病例59989例（武汉市42752例），死亡1789例（武汉市1381例），治愈出院7862例。
A total of 59989 confirmed cases (42,752 in Wuhan) and 1,789 deaths (1,381 in Wuhan) were reported in Hubei Province.
