Wuhan Sports Center Fang Cao Hospital in smooth operation.
该方舱医院2月12日下午起正式收治新冠肺炎轻症患者，提供1100张医疗床位。
Since February 12 afternoon, the hospital has officially admitted new cases of pneumonia with 1,100 beds.
