摄影/中青报·中青网记者赵迪焦点事件▼国家卫生健康委员会发布了《新型冠状病毒肺炎诊疗方案（试行第六版）》。
Why don't we go over to the medical examinationWhy don't we go over to the medical examinationWhy don't we go over to the medical examiner's office.
新方案的诊断标准取消了湖北省和湖北省以外其他省份的区别，统一分为“疑似病例”和“确诊病例”两类，明确确诊病例必须满足核酸检测阳性或基因测序高度同源的证据之一，在治疗方面增加了“康复者血浆治疗”，建议适用于病情进展较快、重型和危重型患者人群。
The diagnostic criteria for the new plan eliminate the differences between provinces other than Hubei and Hubei, and unify them into "suspected cases" and "confirmed cases," clearly identifying cases that must meet one of the evidence of nucleic acid-positive or high genetic sequencing height.
方案增加了“出院后注意事项”，建议应继续进行14天自我健康状况监测。
The programme added "post-discharge precautions" and recommended that the 14-day self-health surveillance should be continued.
还在中医药治疗方面增加了适用于重型、危重型的中成药的具体用法等。
Also in the traditional Chinese medicine treatment for the application of heavy-duty, critical types of Chinese patent medicine specific use.
