摄影/新京报记者陶冉焦点事件▼凌晨，国家卫生健康委员会发布关于修订新冠肺炎英文命名事宜的通知，决定将“新型冠状病毒肺炎”英文名称修订为“COVID-19”，与世界卫生组织命名保持一致，中文名称保持不变。
Shall we change the English name for the new coronavirus pneumonia to COVID-19, consistent with the World Health Organization's nomenclature, the National Health Council announced Monday.
目前，全国疫情发展拐点尚未到来。
At present, the national epidemic development inflection point has not yet arrived.
